##Dictation | if not for this epidemic, this day is the day I put on the show wo suit to get married

WECHAT goodlife225

Functional Introduction, the relentless years, there is love.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Mom always said I had to marry them to get the job done

Dictation / Xiao Meng (Shanghai Graduate School, settled in Shanghai)

My hometown is a small county town in Hubei.

Nine days ago, friends and relatives sent a message: Wuhan City, Small Dream from Shanghai can not come back, the sixth wedding did not get married.
She's about the same age as little dream, but she's practically my niece by birth.
The wedding was called off and the little dreamer is still in Shanghai.
I called my niece, whom I hadn't seen in years, and Xiao Meng told me that her mother had never felt so sad on the day she decided to call off the wedding.

01
Mom says I'm not done until I'm married

If it hadn't been for this epidemic, my husband and I would have been married on the sixth day in my hometown in Hubei Province.

He and I have been talking for more than three years, and we have also bought a house and settled down in Shanghai. Last year we got a license, and we wanted to have the wedding in my hometown first, and then in his hometown. It's festive to get married on New Year's Day.
I was the second child in the family, and my sister had long since married. My mother always said I had to marry them to fulfill their life's mission. Everyone's really excited about this wedding.
My parents both work away from home. My father is in Dongguan and my mother is in Wuchang.

In order to prepare for the wedding, my mother returned home from Wuchang in October.
She had booked a banquet in the county seat early and bought me a new wardrobe and dresser, even though I hadn't lived at home for many years. Mother said, the marriage room simple arrangement, after we go home to pick up the decorations.
Mother also early to relatives sent a message: "The sixth dream in XXX marriage, early to eat wine Ha. "
I called her from time to time to see how the supplies were coming along. Mom says she's got 30 red packets. I said 30 isn't enough, not for the children of relatives and friends.
She smiled and said, I'll get some tomorrow.
She also showed me bought bedding, I dislike the color is not good, she said tomorrow to buy a bright red bed.
At that time, the whole family is immersed in the joy of preparing for the wedding atmosphere.

I put on more than 400 yuan on the Internet to buy the show wo clothes, wear a headdress, take a photo to show them, my sister helped me make an appointment with the makeup artist.
I sent out wedding photos from my family, and they picked out the best ones and had me print them and take them back to Anlu.
I want to call off the wedding. Mom says you can't joke. Sister says you're crazy
Our parents had already prepared everything. We didn't have to worry about much. Our company had a long holiday, so we booked a train ticket in advance for the night of the 12th month (January 22) . We took a sleeper from Shanghai to Hankou and then transferred back to our hometown.
Go home for New Year's Eve dinner, pay respects to relatives for a few days, I will get married.
On January 20, academician Zhong Nanshan said, coronavirus can be transmitted from person to person, and people are urged not to go to Wuhan if they can not. We are beginning to realize the seriousness of the problem.
Thinking of changing trains in Hankou, I started buying face masks online. Medical surgical masks and N95 masks were out of stock in an instant. I only got some disposable face masks.
I called my parents and told them to be careful at home and not to contact anyone who comes back from Wuhan. My father said good, my mother smiled and said nothing, long ago in this matter, are rumors, kindergarten a lot of children caught a cold, soon all better.
The next day at the office, everyone was talking about the new pneumonia. Some online news let me know that the situation in Wuhan may be worse than we thought, I could not help but buy some masks.
Creative intent

That day at the office, my Hung Up, began to hesitate. I'm getting on the bus tomorrow and going home to get married, but, but..
In the evening my mother calls me, nagging told me to leave before the house must be tidied up, remember the power, water and gas.
I waited for her to finish, and said slowly, "mom, I'm still trying to decide if I want to go back. "
The Voice of the mother on the other end of the line changed so quickly that I could see her eyebrows furrowed in Chagrin. "Huh? ! "
"Don't joke with me, it's all ready, you said not to come back? ! "
I couldn't speak. I felt terrible. On the phone, I heard my cute little nephew shouting angrily: "If my aunt doesn't come back, don't come back! "
Little nephew like me, know I will soon go home, a few days in advance of my home, looking forward to my return.
My mother relented a little, and she started to talk to me. She said, you are afraid of Wuhan's disease, then we do not transfer from Wuhan is not all right? You have to come back. You can't cancel a wedding.
She wouldn't listen to me. She insisted the catering was fine.
I had to hang up the phone and ask my sister to help persuade her mother should still be useful.
But I just told my sister I want to call off the wedding. My sister said: "YOU ARE CRAZY! Make a mountain out of a molehill. We can not pull down this face! "
I became an island.
I decided to go home and get married. If I'm really sick, I'll just accept it
I don't have anybody to back me up.
Wake up in the morning, I said to my husband, go home, really do not want to disappoint the family. "If we get it, if we get sick, we accept it, " he said.
Creative intent

We changed our ticket from Hankou to Wuchang, consoling ourselves that things would be better across the river from the seafood market.
Mother's call came again: "Do you return? "
"return a Bar, return of. " The mouth says so, my in the mind still does not want.
By this time Shanghai was already in a state of panic, and the whole day had been particularly trying. I managed to scrounge up some more N95 masks,
The husband began to pack.
Good friend's home is also in Hubei, she decided not to go back, I took the home key to her, let her help take care of our cat Chinese New Year.
I'm going back to get married.

02
I hesitated at the last moment, Dad said not to come back after do not return

This long day has not ended, I am holding the nine o'clock train ticket in my hand, lying in bed, do not want to move, my husband is still packing, although I know he does not want to return.

My mother sent voice message again: "decided to go back to do not hesitate, quickly ready to go! "

We started a new round of fighting. I said that if a banquet infected others, people will be scolded for a lifetime. According to my mom, you're the one who said it was scary and safe.
My father had not said a word before, but this time also directly roared up: "Do not come back after all! " My mother said: "If not back, the man's wedding we do not attend! "
Mom and dad have been good-natured, treat us two sisters have also been very tolerant understanding. For the first time in years, I saw my parents so angry, they waited so long, I let them down.
I hung up the phone and began to cry.
At night, mom asked me if I was in the car. I saw the message. I threw my phone away and never called her back.
She asked my husband, heard the news has been refund, my mother said she has never been so sad.
I'll be sure to put on that suit
Where can I sleep at night. I woke up crying, and at 4:00 in the morning, I woke up again, and this time I couldn't sleep.
I finally turned my phone back on and saw my mother at 12:30 at night in a group of relatives sent a message to tell everyone the wedding was off.
My mother is embarrassed to say that I do not want to go back, with everyone said, is my unit leadership forced refund, it is not back, sorry everyone.

At this time, the news of the closure of Wuhan also came. In the group, the relatives did not say anything, everyone should know the seriousness of the situation.
I thought about it for a long time, and finally I couldn't help but respond to everyone in the group of relatives around 7 am.
I said, really very sorry, just very times, for everyone's health or to cancel, but also hope that people move less, wear masks, wash hands frequently.
When I called my mother again, it was clear that her anger was mostly gone, and this time it really began to sink in.
She told us to take care of ourselves in Shanghai. She's already canceled.
A few days later, many counties and cities in Hubei were closed, and so was my hometown. Parents fully understand us, but also comfort us that thanks to the wedding, the family has a large pile of vegetables, not afraid of no food.
I saw, a few days ago, my mother posted on the Internet our wedding photos video, she said, her little cotton-padded jacket to get married.

Do they still have weddings back home? I don't know. My sister said it was either that or not.
But I knew I would wear the suit.
